  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the outside, people lived, they could see in out-- from the outside that was a camp, that people were killed over there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could smell it, because of the bodies they were burning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was time, many times, even that food what we got from them, we couldn't eat of the smell of the burning bodies.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the lazaret.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the lazaret.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They burned, all the garbage went into that pit, and the bodies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think [NON-ENGLISH] with the children were burning together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a horrible smell, horrible smell, the, the flesh and the stink of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes, very, very sometimes, it happened many times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were asking, are there anything which could be remembered?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The scream of the woman from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could-- you hair could stood up, just listening to the screaming of the people, before they were gassed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The gassing in Treblinka, it was a different one than any places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not only that, the killings were done by a motor to take out the air from the room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That people couldn't have nothing to breathe with.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when they put in the gas, the people were already dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] It was also many, many times [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that people from the working kommando in the camp I, something they did wrong or to them it looked wrong, we, one another, has to drag down to that lazaret.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before the lazaret, there were over there, Ukrainian with a gun, a bullet in the head, and throwing into the lazaret.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
